nodes.title: About CausVid LoRA
widgets_values: We have added CausVid LoRA by default to achieve acceleration. However, in some cases, the video may shake and become blurry. You might need to test different LoRA intensities to get the best results, which should be between 0.3 and 0.7. If you don't need it, you can use the bypass mode to disable it, and then restore the settings of `KSampler` to the default ones.

nodes.title: [EN] About video mask
widgets_values:
Currently, it's difficult to perfectly draw dynamic masks for different frames using only core nodes. However, to avoid requiring users to install additional custom nodes, our templates only use core nodes. You can refer to this implementation idea to achieve video inpainting.

You can use KJNode‚Äôs Points Editor and Sam2Segmentation to create some dynamic mask functions.

Custom node links:
- [ComfyUI-KJNodes](https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-KJNodes)
- [ComfyUI-segment-anything-2](https://github.com/kijai/ComfyUI-segment-anything-2)
